OL,3,CPolice appeal for witnesses after
OL,4,C'suspicious' heath fire near Wareham
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fafter a "suspicious" heath fire near
OL,8,FWareham at the weekend.
OL,10,FThe fire broke out on Saturday 4 July
OL,11,Fin Bere Road in the Coldharbour area.
OL,13,FThere were no reports of any injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
