OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783680590
OL,3,CPolice appeal for witnesses after
OL,4,C'suspicious' heath fire near Wareham
OL,6,FCrews from Wareham, Redhill Park,
OL,7,FChristchurch, Westbourne, Wimborne,
OL,8,FSwanage and Springbourne attended
OL,9,Falong with lightweight off-road
OL,10,Fvehicles from Bere Regis, Swanage,
OL,11,FHamworthy, Poole, three water carriers
OL,12,Ffrom Poole, Wareham and Ringwood
OL,13,F(Hampshire & Isle of Wight Fire and
OL,14,FRescue Service) and a command unit
OL,15,Ffrom Gillingham.
OL,17,FFirefighters used multiple hose reel
OL,18,Fjets and main lines to extinguish the
OL,19,Fflames.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
