CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783680590
OL,3,CPolice appeal for witnesses after
OL,4,C'suspicious' heath fire near Wareham
OL,6,FThe incident was then scaled back to
OL,7,Ffour relief appliances from
OL,8,FSturminster Newton, Dorchester,
OL,9,FShaftesbury and Ferndown and the stop
OL,10,Fcame in at 5.49pm.
OL,12,FThe service urged members of the
OL,13,Fpublic to avoid the area during the
OL,14,Foperation.
OL,16,FLater in the evening it said
OL,17,Ffirefighters were dampening down
OL,18,Fhotspots, and were treating the fire
OL,19,Fas deliberate.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
