OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783680590
OL,3,CPolice appeal for witnesses after
OL,4,C'suspicious' heath fire near Wareham
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Darren Stanton, of
OL,7,FDorset County CID, said: "We are
OL,8,Fworking with the fire service to
OL,9,Festablish how this fire was started.
OL,11,F"I would urge anyone who saw any
OL,12,Fsuspicious activity in the area during
OL,13,Fthe afternoon of Saturday 4 July 2026
OL,14,Fto please get in touch."
